== Bugs
$ gsr clean ext/swim-pgx/
git-subrepo: command failed: git config remote.subrepo/ext/swim-pgx.url




== Pull strategy

1) clone .git into tmp dir .git/subrepo
2) Either:
   a) check upstream for ./foo/
   b) git subrepo pull ./foo/ (upstream)
3) filter-branch subdir foo
3) Find commit range from last time
4) Try to rebase onto foo
5) push upstream
6) cleanup. rm -fr .git/subrepo
7) say done



== Try this:

Take a history:

    a→b→c→d

Split into:

    a→b and c→d

Add commit:

    a→b→e

Rewrite commits:

    c'→d'

add:

    c'→d'→f

Rebase:

    a→b→e→c'→d'→f

What happens?
